From: Jaehoon Lee <jaehoon85.lee@lge.com>
Date: Wed, 19 Nov 2025 14:06:56 +0900
Subject: gst-play: Add missing unlock for invalid track type

Add missing unlock in play_cycle_track_selection
of gst-play. The unlock should be added when
the function ends in an exceptional case.

Part-of: <https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/gstreamer/gstreamer/-/merge_requests/10144>
---
 tools/gst-play.c | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/tools/gst-play.c b/tools/gst-play.c
index f492f52..9b21f3c 100644
--- a/tools/gst-play.c
+++ b/tools/gst-play.c
@@ -1289,6 +1289,7 @@ play_cycle_track_selection (GstPlay * play, GstPlayTrackType track_type,
       }
       break;
     default:
+      g_mutex_unlock (&play->selection_lock);
       return;
   }
 
